(8th day of 4th month
of 3rd year of Xuantong)

2
00:00:13,958 --> 00:00:16,128
(Grain in Ear is 32 days away.)

3
00:00:18,560 --> 00:00:24,384
(Cotton Alley, Shuntian)

4
00:00:34,336 --> 00:00:34,880
Hurry up.

5
00:00:34,880 --> 00:00:35,520
Hurry up.

6
00:00:37,799 --> 00:00:39,119
Run.

7
00:00:43,119 --> 00:00:44,079
Don't move.

8
00:00:56,032 --> 00:00:58,138
(Long Zhen Li Jiu
will change the nation at harvest time.)

9
00:01:02,720 --> 00:01:03,240
Sir.

10
00:01:03,240 --> 00:01:04,680
We found two boxes of gunpowder inside.

11
00:01:04,879 --> 00:01:06,120
Take these rebels

12
00:01:06,640 --> 00:01:07,480
back to yamen.

13
00:01:25,280 --> 00:01:27,239
Are you a Reformist?

14
00:01:28,280 --> 00:01:29,439
I am.

15
00:01:30,159 --> 00:01:32,439
I am going to take down
all flunkies like you

16
00:01:32,519 --> 00:01:34,439
and overthrow the Qing Imperial Court.

17
00:01:34,760 --> 00:01:37,400
You are under my control now.

18
00:01:37,400 --> 00:01:39,519
If you don't want to die...

19
00:01:41,439 --> 00:01:43,040
There are quite a few like you.

20
00:01:43,719 --> 00:01:44,480
Scared of death?

21
00:01:45,400 --> 00:01:46,280
Scared of death?

22
00:01:46,760 --> 00:01:48,519
I won't join the Reform if I am.

23
00:01:48,959 --> 00:01:50,400
Kill me now,

24
00:01:50,640 --> 00:01:52,200
and I wouldn't even blink.

25
00:01:52,480 --> 00:01:53,879
It doesn't matter if I die.

26
00:01:54,239 --> 00:01:56,680
There will be other comrades

27
00:01:56,680 --> 00:01:58,319
carrying on the cause
I have not completed.

28
00:01:59,799 --> 00:02:01,120
That sounds very familiar.

29
00:02:01,879 --> 00:02:04,040
Many people have said this
since ancient times.

30
00:02:05,519 --> 00:02:06,640
Yes, you're right.

31
00:02:07,079 --> 00:02:08,199
That's how we are.

32
00:02:08,352 --> 00:02:08,919
Right?

33
00:02:08,919 --> 00:02:10,360
Life and death are natural,

34
00:02:10,360 --> 00:02:12,439
just a breath away.

35
00:02:12,439 --> 00:02:14,599
Death really isn't so awful.

36
00:02:14,599 --> 00:02:16,280
There are many things
more awful than death.

37
00:02:17,000 --> 00:02:18,080
Torture him a bit.

38
00:02:18,479 --> 00:02:19,919
Show these people

39
00:02:19,919 --> 00:02:21,800
what is more awful than death.

40
00:02:21,800 --> 00:02:24,719
You will wish you were dead by then.

41
00:02:25,120 --> 00:02:28,360
I don't believe that no one cracks.

42
00:02:28,639 --> 00:02:30,840
You devil.

43
00:02:30,840 --> 00:02:32,520
You won't end up well.

44
00:02:32,520 --> 00:02:36,479
The first person who confesses
will be spared.

45
00:02:36,840 --> 00:02:39,319
The rest will end up like him.

46
00:02:39,840 --> 00:02:40,439
Got it.

47
00:02:40,599 --> 00:02:42,759
You devil, how dare you?

48
00:02:42,759 --> 00:02:43,319
Whip him.

49
00:02:43,319 --> 00:02:44,120
You devil.

50
00:02:47,680 --> 00:02:48,240
Talk.

51
00:02:50,199 --> 00:02:50,840
Talk!

52
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:51,879
Confess!

53
00:02:51,879 --> 00:02:52,840
Come on!

54
00:02:56,960 --> 00:02:57,759
Talk!

55
00:02:58,120 --> 00:02:58,919
Aren't you tough?

56
00:03:01,680 --> 00:03:02,400
Talk!

57
00:03:03,960 --> 00:03:04,800
Confess!

58
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:12,000
I confess!

59
00:03:12,000 --> 00:03:13,080
I am willing to confess.

60
00:03:13,080 --> 00:03:15,479
Sir!

61
00:03:15,639 --> 00:03:16,240
Sir!

62
00:03:16,240 --> 00:03:17,199
Sir, I will confess.

63
00:03:17,199 --> 00:03:19,199
I will tell you everything, sir!

64
00:03:19,199 --> 00:03:19,712
Talk.

65
00:03:27,080 --> 00:03:28,560
Do I have to ask?

66
00:03:29,879 --> 00:03:30,680
Talk!

67
00:03:31,360 --> 00:03:32,319
Sir.

68
00:03:32,759 --> 00:03:34,840
We were indeed planning a rebellion.

69
00:03:36,840 --> 00:03:37,879
Long Zhen Li Jiu

70
00:03:38,479 --> 00:03:39,680
will change the nation at harvest time.

71
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:41,879
This is a rumor they spread.

72
00:03:42,080 --> 00:03:45,280
They want to confuse you

73
00:03:45,360 --> 00:03:46,199
and make you believe

74
00:03:46,199 --> 00:03:49,159
the rebellion will be on Grain in Ear,
the 11th day of May.

75
00:03:52,439 --> 00:03:55,000
So when will it be actually?

76
00:03:55,479 --> 00:03:57,360
Actually, we will take action

77
00:03:57,360 --> 00:04:00,199
on the night of the 29th day
of the 4th month.

78
00:04:00,680 --> 00:04:04,400
Nine groups of rebel forces
will launch attacks

79
00:04:05,039 --> 00:04:08,800
from the west, south,
and north of the city.

80
00:04:09,599 --> 00:04:10,280
Nine groups?

81
00:04:11,759 --> 00:04:12,680
How many people in total?

82
00:04:13,960 --> 00:04:16,759
I've heard there would be
about 300 people.

83
00:04:16,759 --> 00:04:17,560
You've heard?

84
00:04:18,079 --> 00:04:20,319
That's what I know, sir.

85
00:04:20,720 --> 00:04:22,639
We just acted on orders.

86
00:04:22,639 --> 00:04:23,720
Whose orders?

87
00:04:24,160 --> 00:04:25,079
Tongmenghui.

88
00:04:25,079 --> 00:04:26,439
Tongmenghui.

89
00:04:26,439 --> 00:04:28,759
You are one of them?

90
00:04:28,759 --> 00:04:31,199
No.

91
00:04:31,319 --> 00:04:32,680
We aren't.

92
00:04:32,680 --> 00:04:34,839
We just work for Tongmenghui.

93
00:04:35,168 --> 00:04:35,680
Sir.

94
00:04:35,680 --> 00:04:37,000
I shouldn't have done this.

95
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:39,199
Please tell me what to do.

96
00:04:39,199 --> 00:04:41,319
Please tell me what to do.

97
00:04:41,319 --> 00:04:42,560
I am begging you.

98
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:43,839
Please tell me.

99
00:04:43,839 --> 00:04:44,480
Drag him away.

100
00:04:44,480 --> 00:04:45,399
Get him out of here.

101
00:04:45,519 --> 00:04:46,879
Please spare my life.

102
00:04:46,879 --> 00:04:47,839
Sir.

103
00:04:48,399 --> 00:04:49,759
Please spare my life.

104
00:04:50,560 --> 00:04:52,079
Please spare my life.

